title: "The Allie Scenario Prompting Protocol: A Scenario-Constrained, Outcome-First Method for Prompt Engineering"
type: report

authors:
  - family-names: "Allie"
    given-names: "Darren L."
    affiliation: "Azure & Verdant Vistas, LLC"

abstract: "The Allie Scenario Prompting Protocol (ASPP) is a scenario-constrained, outcome-first prompt engineering methodology created by Darren L. Allie, Director of AI Workflow Optimization and AI Business Improvement, Azure & Verdant Vistas, LLC. ASPP is designed to produce one best actionable output through structured reasoning, constraint analysis, decision narrowing, and executable action planning to reduce brainstorming noise."

